channel.title: Compiling Error, Someone Please Help!
channel.description:
When I hit compile on my source, It just says:
'"F:\Program Files(x86) Java/jdk1.6.0_18/bin/javac"' is not recognized as an internal or external command, operable program or batch file.
Can someone please let me know what to do, and before you say what's (x86)? I have windows 7, and I have 2 sets of Program files, and The Java folder is set up in the Program Files (x86)
Can someone please let me know how to fix this..
